</taxonomicName>
differing in the obtuse sepals. Specimens from Aguascalientes are somewhat intermediate with 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" genus="Ipomoea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="durangensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Ipomoea durangensis</emphasis>
